<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾；Best effort，你呢？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>@詳細Template@</strong></span><br />\n每日任務。每星期任務。每月任務。<br />\n日日update<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1559163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1559163</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\nVersion 2019.09.20"},{"pid":"feee7159c91b25c6fd89bf8e9b4cbfb2eb6ea32a","tid":1582963,"uid":287713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c87ef485013c4a844d5f412a6f74a14bfd4aa43","tid":1582963,"uid":51840,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T11:33:34.000Z","msg":"告條on9仔叛國罪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:20:13.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n證據確鑿<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e6e0686676dde6f84ae646c0707b26f9a358dd","tid":1582963,"uid":169116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:21:42.000Z","msg":"高獨之父"},{"pid":"44fc551017b27b369cbd29a64ddc13b62aba20d6","tid":1582963,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:21:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"127a666d66582cf723ec9f714442b19c476d7650","tid":1582963,"uid":181156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:23:34.000Z","msg":"如果佢搞高獨我支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b2e5a36e03c823422aeb23a0d1bc2fd30e057f","tid":1582963,"uid":62409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:24:49.000Z","msg":"係咪想好似北愛咁"},{"pid":"1eb0911963d87850d195bad653d7ad6296c3aa08","tid":1582963,"uid":259674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:25:10.000Z","msg":"即係想死啫<br />\n蔡英文又有子彈啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6ddd815e62a3ceb98f453ac87627431ae62a0d","tid":1582963,"uid":126046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:25:54.000Z","msg":"獨立啦"},{"pid":"2e9f46a8345244cd216c2c42b6ae6d5c55dda922","tid":1582963,"uid":39838,